| Source Directories

If "<NCMail$Dir>" = "" Then Error 0 NCMail dir not setup.

Set NCMailRes$Path <NCMail$Dir>.
Set NCMailRes$Dir <NCMail$Dir>
|
| Output Directory
Set NCMailOutput$Dir RAM::RamDisc0.$
Set NCMailOutput$Path RAM::RamDisc0.$.
|
| Create RAM Disc.
changedynamicarea -RamFSSize 200K

| Setup POP3 details.
Set Inet$EmailAddress nbingham@acorn.com
Set Inet$EmailRealName Neil Bingham

|Set Inet$EmailPOP3User pop3test
|Set Inet$EmailPOP3Password pop3test
Set Inet$EmailPOP3User nbtest
Set Inet$EmailPOP3Password pop3test

Set Inet$EmailPOP3Hostname rwarren
Set Inet$EmailSMTPHostname rwarren

Set DebugLib$Device_NCMail 6

Set NCFresco$Screen 0,0,1280,960
